e: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: start;\">August 3, 2023<\/p><\/span>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-730e9001 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"730e9001\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; font-family: Georgia, Times; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 100%; color: #1a4f4f; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: start;\">Now, WHO-GMP standards have been seamlessly integrated into the revised Schedule M.<\/p><p>In a significant move to elevate the quality management standards of\u00a0<strong>Indian pharmaceutical manufacturers<\/strong>, the Health Ministry has unveiled a crucial initiative for the\u00a0<strong>revised schedule M<\/strong>.<\/p><p><strong>As per Notification: G.S.R. 922(E) dated 28.12.2023, the new set of rules as per revised Schedule M guidelines must be implemented by pharma companies with turnover &lt;=250 crores within 12 months from the date of publication (5.1.2024).<\/strong><\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a325240 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"a325240\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"325\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/newsclip.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/newsclip.jpg 500w, http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/newsclip-300x195.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4682a627 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"4682a627\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e234c3b elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"e234c3b\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-be1d615 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"be1d615\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><h5><strong>2. Draft Guidelines for GMP in Cosmetics introduced by US Food and Drug Administration.\u00a0<\/strong><\/h5><div><h3 style=\"font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; color: #1a4f4f; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: auto; font-size: 1.625rem; letter-spacing: 0.5px; max-width: 100%; font-style: normal; text-align: start;\">What&#8217;s New<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: auto; font-family: Georgia, Times; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 100%; color: #1a4f4f; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: start;\">May 3, 2023<\/p><p style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; font-family: Georgia, Times; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 100%; color: #1a4f4f; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: start;\">FDA intends to withdraw or revise and reissue this draft guidance as appropriate, based on the GMP rulemaking required by the Modernization of Cosmetics Regulation\u00a0 Act (MOCRA) of 2022.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-429f536 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"429f536\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"365\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/cosmetics_GMP_flash1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/cosmetics_GMP_flash1.jpg 500w, http:\/\/localhost\/wordpress\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/cosmetics_GMP_flash1-300x219.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>1. New Draft Proposals for a Revised Schedule M published by Central Drugs Standard Control Organization, Directorate General of Health Services, Ministry of Health &amp; FW, Government of India. 1) Revised Schedule M: Govt sets deadline for pharma industry August 3, 2023 Now, WHO-GMP standards have been seamlessly integrated into the revised Schedule M. In &hellip;<\/p>\n<p class=\"read-more\"> <a c